snippet.textDisplay:
That new character, it could be Heath, Connie, Maggie, or Morgan. Morgan is on FearTWD so I doubt it’s him. Maggie is back, but in the ending scene she has the same color shirt/coat, but I’d wearing a hat and no gloves (unless she took em off) but heath hasn’t been back in a while and Connie couldn’t learn skills like that so quickly. It has to be either Heath or Maggie. Most likely Maggie. The legs are skinny, and the jeans are also skinny: girl clothing. But if it’s Heath, I’m so hyped. Or it could be a new character which would be badass.

Edit: they also have a hood, so maybe it isn’t Maggie. Why would she change clothes as her friends are being attacked? And I looked at the pants again, and they could be a guy honestly. I’m seriously hoping it’s Heath. Most likely a new character.

Another edit lmao: when they stepped, their pant leg came up and their skin was white. They are definitely new.
